assists for his 10th career triple-double as the Seattle SuperSonics clinched
seventh place in the Western Conference with a 119-112 overtime victory over the
Sacramento Kings on Tuesday night. Seattle secured the playoff spot with one
game left in the season by having a better conference record than the
eighth-place Kings.
</P>
