   April 27: Actor Jack Klugman is 78. Singer Cuba Gooding of the
Main Ingredient is 56. Musician Ace Frehley of Kiss is 49. Singer
Sheena Easton is 41. Musician Rob Squires of Big Head Todd and the
Monsters is 35. Singer Mica Paris is 31. Singer-musician Travis
